txt.en: 'You there, maggot! You are needed to defend our forces in Forochel. The Free Worms are struggling a bit much for our lazy lads.\n\n'I need to you to hunt out some of the most dangerous of our enemies: the Lore-masters.'
The Free Peoples are fighting back against the invasion of the Iron Crown.
You have been instructed to defeat Lore-masters in Forochel.
Complete your slaughter before today's invasion ends
